Mini Project: Voting System in Python
📌 Objective
To develop a simple console-based Voting System using Python programming.
📋 Project Requirements (Mandatory)
1. Create at least 3 candidates.
2. Allow users to cast their vote.
3. Count the votes properly.
4. Display the final result.
5. Create a menu-driven program.
6. Include an exit option.

